tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE market_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(10),
    price DECIMAL,
    volume INT,
    trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trades (
  trade_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol STRING,
  trade_type STRING,
  trade_price DECIMAL,
  trade_volume INT,
  trade_timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE indicators (
  indicator_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol STRING,
  indicator_type STRING,
  indicator_value DECIMAL,
  timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE models (
  model_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name STRING,
  model_type STRING,
  model_accuracy DECIMAL,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    symbol VARCHAR(10),
    open_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    high_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    low_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    close_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    symbol VARCHAR(10),
    trade_type VARCHAR(10),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE feature_engineering (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    symbol VARCHAR(10),
    feature_1 DECIMAL(10, 2),
    feature_2 DECIMAL(10, 2),
    feature_3 DECIMAL(10, 2),
    target DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE model_results (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    symbol VARCHAR(10),
    model_name VARCHAR(20),
    accuracy DECIMAL(5, 4),
    profit_loss DECIMAL(10, 2)
);
